Cell["\<\
Phenotypic lag model for STRmutS.  One resistant allele. 
Mixed strains AD30mutS and AD30YFPmutS .\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8844400597703557`*^9, 3.884440069902989*^9}, {
